{{Infobox artwork | title = July Reflections | image = July Reflections.jpg | image_size = | artist = Martha Burchfield | year = 1972 | type = Watercolor | height_inch = 18 7/8 | width_inch = 24 | dimensions = 18 7/8 x 24 in. | museum = Burchfield Penny Art Center | city = Buffalo | url = {{url|https://www.burchfieldpenney.org/exhibitions/exhibition:04-17-1977-07-31-1977-martha-burchfield-richter-1924-1977-memorial-tribute/|Martha Burchfield Richter (1924-1977): Memorial Tribute}} }} '''''July Reflections''''' is a [[Watercolor painting|watercolor]] on seamed paper by [[Martha Elizabeth Burchfield Richter|Martha Burchfield]] that she made in 1972 in [[Buffalo, New York]] based on a pencil sketch.<ref>{{cite web|title=Martha Burchfield Richter (1924-1977): Memorial Tribute|url=https://www.burchfieldpenney.org/exhibitions/exhibition:04-17-1977-07-31-1977-martha-burchfield-richter-1924-1977-memorial-tribute/|publisher=[[Burchfield Penney Art Center]]|accessdate=26 September 2016}}</ref>
