== Winners ==
=== Prix Versailles 2015 === The awards were conferred at [[UNESCO]] Headquarters on 19 June 2015.<ref>[http://www.lsa-conso.fr/les-galeries-lafayette-de-marseille-laureate-du-1er-prix-versailles,213672 {{fr}} Les Galeries Lafayette de Marseille lauréate du 1er prix Versailles]</ref><ref>[http://diversum.net/fichiers/File/%28en%29_DP_Prix_Versailles.pdf Press kit from 22 June 2015] (accessed on 24 August 2016).</ref> After a first edition specific to France, the prix was expanded to the rest of the world in 2016. {| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center; width: 100%;" ! width="10%" | Prix or special prize || width="10%" | Category || width="22%" | Project || width="16%" | Location || width="10%" | Country || width="22%" | Architect or designer || width="10%" | Country |- | Prix Versailles | | ''[[Galeries Lafayette]], Centre Bourse''<ref>[http://www.directmatin.fr/patrimoine/2015-06-21/un-prix-recompense-les-plus-beaux-commerces-706334 {{fr}} Un prix récompense les plus beaux commerces]</ref><ref>[http://www.cyberarchi.com/article/prix-versailles-architecture-commerciale-quatre-projets-laureats-25-06-2015-15612 {{fr}} Prix Versailles Architecture Commerciale : quatre projets lauréats]</ref> | [[Marseille]] | France | ''Moatti – Rivière''<ref>[http://www.batir-jcsr.ch/magOnline.php?mag=9617 {{fr}} Bâtir – Journal de la construction de la Suisse romande]</ref> | France |- | Special prize Interior | | ''Brasserie Les Haras''<ref>[http://batijournal.com/haras-de-strasbourg-recompenses/88026 {{fr}} Les Haras de Strasbourg récompensés]</ref> | [[Strasbourg]] | France | ''Jouin Manku'' | France |- | Special prize Exterior | | ''[[Repetto]] shop, rue de Charonne'' | [[Paris]] | France | | |- | Special prize Services | | ''[[Musée des Confluences]] shop'' | [[Lyon]] | France | ''Julien Kolmont de Rogier''<ref>[https://www.amc-archi.com/article/julien-kolmont-de-rogier-laureat-du-prix-versailles-de-l-architecture-commerciale-mention-service,2127 {{fr}} Julien Kolmont de Rogier, lauréat du prix Versailles de l’architecture commerciale mention service]</ref> | France |}
=== Prix Versailles 2016 === The awards were conferred at [[UNESCO]] Headquarters on 27 May 2016.<ref>[http://batinfo.com/actualite/prix-versailles-2016-a-lunesco-neuf-laureats-dans-le-monde-entier_5314 {{fr}} Prix Versailles 2016 à l’UNESCO, neuf lauréats dans le monde entier]</ref><ref>[http://fr.fashionmag.com/news/Le-Prix-Versailles-s-ouvre-a-l-international,688680.html {{fr}} Le Prix Versailles s’ouvre à l’international]</ref> There were nine winners in three categories.<ref>[http://www.businessimmo.com/contents/70748/prix-versailles-2016-9-laureats-dans-le-monde-entier {{fr}} Prix Versailles 2016 : 9 lauréats dans le monde entier]</ref><ref>[http://media.wix.com/ugd/840afa_fa91f26046c64bb3bf10eb830f333130.pdf Press kit from 30 May 2016] (accessed on 24 August 2016)</ref> {| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center; width: 100%;" ! width="10%" | Prix or special prize || width="10%" | Category || width="22%" | Project || width="16%" | Location || width="10%" | Country || width="22%" | Architect or designer || width="10%" | Country |- | Prix Versailles | Shops & Stores | ''[[Alexander McQueen (brand)|Alexander McQueen]]''<ref>[http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/alexander-mcqueen-prix-versailles-10439871/ Alexander McQueen Store Wins Prix Versailles]</ref><ref>[http://www.themalaymailonline.com/features/article/alexander-mcqueens-paris-store-wins-design-award Alexander McQueen’s Paris store wins design award]</ref><ref>[http://www.retailwatching.nl/formules/artikel/XvomSRbAQeWNkpjFsZ_whw-1/het-prijswinnende-vlaggenschip-van-alexander-mcqueen.html {{nl}} Het prijswinnende vlaggenschip van Alexander McQueen]</ref> | [[Paris]] | France | ''[[David Collins (interior designer)|David Collins]] Studio'' | United Kingdom |- | Special prize Interior | Shops & Stores | ''Ganjam'' | [[Bangalore]] | India | ''RDAI'' | France |- | Special prize Exterior | Shops & Stores | ''TOG – [[Philippe Starck]]'' | [[São Paulo]] | Brazil | ''Triptyque'' | Brazil |- | Prix Versailles | Hotels | ''Phum Baitang'' | [[Siem Reap]] | Cambodia | ''AW²'' | France |- | Special prize Interior | Hotels | ''Les Bains'' | [[Paris]] | France | ''Tristan Auer'' | France |- | Special prize Exterior | Hotels | ''Dasavatara Hotel'' | [[Tirupati]] | India | ''SJK Architects'' | India |- | Prix Versailles | Restaurants | ''Dasavatara – Lotus Cafe'' | [[Tirupati]] | India | ''SJK Architects'' | India |- | Special prize Interior | Restaurants | ''L'Amico'' | [[New York City]] | United States | ''Jun Aizaki Architecture & Design'' | United States |- | Special prize Exterior | Restaurants | ''Hanoi Cà Phê'' | [[Paris]] | France | ''Officine Architecture'' | France |- |}
=== Prix Versailles 2017 – World winners === The awards were conferred at [[UNESCO]] Headquarters on 12 May 2017. Twelve world winners were recognized in four categories, selected from amongst 70 continental winners from 35 countries.<ref>[http://www.archdaily.com/873613/prix-versailles-celebrates-12-projects-for-their-outstanding-commercial-architecture Prix Versailles Celebrates 12 Projects for Their Outstanding Commercial Architecture]</ref><ref>[http://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/840afa_fa7df78371d84e388cd213917afb15ee.pdf Press release from 15 May 2017] (accessed on 27 July 2017)</ref> {| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center; width: 100%;" ! width="10%" | Prix or special prize || width="10%" | Category || width="22%" | Project || width="16%" | Location || width="10%" | Country || width="22%" | Architect or designer || width="10%" | Country |- | Prix Versailles | Shops & Stores | ''[[Dior]] Miami'' | [[Miami]] | United States | ''BarbaritoBancel architectes'' | France |- | Special prize Interior | Shops & Stores | ''Hangzhou Zhongshuge'' | [[Hangzhou]] | China | ''X+Living'' | China |- | Special prize Exterior | Shops & Stores | ''[[Chanel]] – temporary store'' | [[Amsterdam]] | Netherlands | ''[[MVRDV]]'' | Netherlands |- | Prix Versailles | Shopping Malls | ''Tokyu Plaza Ginza'' | [[Tokyo]] | Japan | ''[[Nikken Sekkei]]'' | Japan |- | Special prize Interior | Shopping Malls | ''ARG Shopping Mall'' | [[Tehran]] | Iran | ''arsh4d studio'' | Iran |- | Special prize Exterior | Shopping Malls | ''Lideta Mercato'' | [[Addis Ababa]] | Ethiopia | ''[[Xavier Vilalta|Vilalta Arquitectura]]'' | Spain |- | Prix Versailles | Hotels | ''Chablé – Yucatan Peninsula'' | [[Chocholá Municipality]] | Mexico | ''Jorge Borja, Paulina Morán'' | Mexico |- | Special prize Interior | Hotels | ''Spedition'' | [[Thun]] | Switzerland | ''Stylt Trampoli'' | Sweden |- | Special prize Exterior | Hotels | ''Mar Adentro'' | [[San José del Cabo]] | Mexico | ''Miguel Ángel Aragonés'' | Mexico 