=== Prix Versailles 2018 – Continental winners === The continental awards were conferred: * on 14 April 2018 in [[Santiago de Chile]] (Castillo Hidalgo)<ref>[http://www.t13.cl/noticia/tendencias/chile-sera-sede-uno-premios-referentes-nivel-mundial-arquitectura-comercial/ {{es}} Chile será sede de uno de los premios referentes a nivel mundial en arquitectura comercial] (accessed on 18 August 2018)</ref> for the Central America, the South and the Caribbean region and the North America region;<ref>[https://www.archdaily.com/892541/continental-winners-of-prix-versailles-2018-highlights-22-built-projects-for-their-outstanding-commercial-architecture 22 Projects Named Continental Winners of Prix Versailles 2018] (accessed on 18 August 2018)</ref><ref>[http://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/840afa_279f16751a814f44b8f2fa3e77566588.pdf Press release from 16 April 2018] (accessed on 18 August 2018)</ref> * on 20 April 2018 in [[Beijing]] ([[Miyun District]]) for the Central Asia and the Northeast region and the South Asia and the Pacific region;<ref>[http://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/840afa_90e9ca96c32347868e851fc8f4f75920.pdf Press release from 21 April 2018] (accessed on 18 August 2018)</ref> * on 26 April 2018 in [[Algiers]] (''Centre international de conférences'') for the Africa and West Asia region and the Europe region.<ref>[https://www.archdaily.com/894153/prix-versailles-celebrates-24-projects-for-their-outstanding-commercial-architecture-in-africa-west-asia-and-europe Prix Versailles Celebrates 24 Projects for Their Outstanding Commercial Architecture in Africa, West Asia and Europe] (accessed on 18 August 2018)</ref><ref>[http://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/840afa_b06e57e53f1e4185aeffd9682353e9fc.pdf Press release from 27 April 2018] (accessed on 18 August 2018)</ref>
